  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/06757a17d7c99011e0407bddd45643da.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=100 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not doubt! This scarecrow-like thing is the incarnation of a god! Assign your villagers to automatically collect the resources needed for settlement development, or you can personally carry a dozen logs!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/af2f2ebf846305662e72f0781ba89a61.poster.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/af2f2ebf846305662e72f0781ba89a61.webm?t=1737439493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/c81a35dd6ac763cbf92e95b08384cab4.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your territory, build houses for your people. And make them work for you! Don't forge to build extravagant solid gold statues to praise your wise leadership! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/f08477d7e78b6cf8892d7cbf831cfb6a.poster.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/f08477d7e78b6cf8892d7cbf831cfb6a.webm?t=1737439493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/bb5654bf10a1242297ca02c6d07b12e7.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See these laser towers, built specifically to roast kobolds! There are also turrets and archery towers you can use to defend your home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/05aba887a069fdb33f96818eaac5cd68.poster.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/05aba887a069fdb33f96818eaac5cd68.webm?t=1737439493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/9f3a282640d953b7f1cf8e4dc938d565.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allocate manpower according to your needs (or pure bad taste), and you can even make your creation work 23 hours a day!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/6ba25fd8a35c49df1cd35c4f0ddb9e97.poster.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/6ba25fd8a35c49df1cd35c4f0ddb9e97.webm?t=1737439493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/6ac4eaac19050cdd331b40d9a5343315.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your army to face the invasion of darkness, transform into a warrior or archer and join the battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/97940c12441716b15c1ce0160b9df352.poster.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/97940c12441716b15c1ce0160b9df352.webm?t=1737439493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/75f8be74124bcf2cf6e3d636f19b7a00.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=100 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 49 kinds of divine powers for you to explore: make traps to hunt goblins, summon fire rain and lightning to torture monsters. And even cast magical magic to change the landscape! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/90ec9be983f31d9768f9d9e935d057a1.poster.avif?t=1737439493\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2607160/extras/90ec9be983f31d9768f9d9e935d057a1.webm?t=1737439493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're interested in Scarecropia, Please WISHLIST to support us! You can also join our  to share your experience!</p>",
